N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 160.36 - Practical examiners

State Regulations

Every practical examiner shall be a New York State
licensed, practicing cosmetologist, natural hair stylist, esthetician, nail
specialist or waxer who has five or more years of active experience in the
related discipline. Notes
